{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"22999-raanmaanjar-raanmaanjar","title":"रानमांजर! रानमांजर!","description":"भेटूया भारतातल्या तऱ्हतऱ्हेच्या रानमांजरांना!","language":"Marathi","langCode":"mr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mrinalinee  Vanarase"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/22999-raanmaanjar-raanmaanjar"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722383/size3/b67b65b0b4e07eecc3cd0aa184e1548c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722383/size6/b67b65b0b4e07eecc3cd0aa184e1548c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48623/size6/8c837e2790a2a776373a80fa987f0cf9.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरांच्या पाठीवर पट्टे असतात.\nजसं की वाघ!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48624/size6/6ea91ca34bdbfc039fb6fdb69747f06c.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरांना आयाळ असते.\nजसं की सिंह!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48625/size6/98d89dc02165b900a45427fc94e73369.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरांच्या अंगावर ठिपके असतात.\nजसं की बिबट्या आणि बिबट्या मांजर!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48626/size6/61f26c636cfb7774c734cb0201b21434.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरं झाडावर पटकन चढू शकतात.\nजसं की धूमिल बिबट्या अन् संगमरवरी मांजर!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48627/size6/380edf3b9b22e6a29483061b0daaa2d1.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरं उंच पर्वतात राहतात.\nजसं की हिम बिबट्या अन् \nपल्ला मांजर!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48628/size6/abcf82b334b1c3312e9c154b53c74755.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरं वाळवंटात राहतात.\nजसं की वाळवंटी मांजर!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48629/size6/e155294059bc64e40c3d85db7e1dc8c6.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरांना केसाळ कान असतात.\nजसं की शशकर्ण आणि पहाड मांजर!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48630/size6/66f9b62c88bc008a4d7fea2df3f28763.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरांना मासेमारी करायला खूप आवडतं.\nजसं मासेमार मांजरं!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48632/size6/d18d79f2ff91aebfa45ae8ef2cc6f0cd.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरं म्हणजे जगातली अगदी छोटी मांजरं.\nजसं की वाघाटी!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48633/size6/5eeceb3f40b3e6a2e1c14ef23faec0a4.jpg","text":"काही रानमांजरं तर अगदी घरातल्या मनीमाऊसारखी दिसतात,\nजसं की जंगली मांजर आणि सोनेरी मांजर!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48634/size6/7c01994016872d0d4908eccc906da432.jpg","text":"पण ती सगळी असतात तर रानमांजरंच ना!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":110}}